    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you ready to fall in love with your next ride? I\u2019m parting with my absolute stunner of a car, and let me tell you, it is in truly incredible, like-new condition! I\u2019ve babied this beauty since the day I got it\u2014it\u2019s been garage-kept, meticulously cleaned, and looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor. It drives like a dream and is completely spotless inside and out. You won't find a single flaw on this one! I'm so excited for someone new to get behind the wheel and enjoy it as much as I have. Drop me a message if you want to come see it!",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
