    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true masterpiece of preservation, presenting in absolute showroom condition. Finished in a deep, mirror-like metallic paint that has been professionally ceramic-coated, the exterior is completely free of stone chips, swirls, or imperfections. Inside, the cabin remains a sanctuary of luxury; the premium leather upholstery still retains its factory scent and shows zero signs of wear or bolster compression. Every electronic component, from the high-fidelity sound system to the advanced driver assistance features, functions flawlessly. Mechanically, the car is impeccable, having been serviced exclusively at authorized dealerships with a comprehensive binder of records included. It has been strictly garage-kept under a breathable cover and has never seen inclement weather. For the discerning collector or enthusiast who demands nothing less than perfection, this is the finest example currently on the market.",
