      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my absolute pride and joy, and let me tell you, she is a total beauty! This car has been my absolute baby\u2014always garaged, meticulously detailed, and kept in truly stunning condition. It honestly looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s been loved and cared for with zero compromises, this is the one. It drives like a dream and is ready for a new home. Come take a look, you won't be disappointed!",
      "price": 44500.0,
